# Terragrunt
**/.terragrunt-cache/*
.terragrunt-cache/

# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfstate.backup
crash.log
crash.*.log
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
.terraform.lock.hcl
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Terragrunt-generated files — auto-created by the root `generate` blocks in
# live/terragrunt.hcl on every `terragrunt init`/`plan`/`apply`. Never commit
# these — they're regenerated fresh every run, and committing a stale copy
# can mask real config drift.
backend.tf
provider.tf

# AWS / credentials
.aws/
kubeconfig
kubeconfig.yaml
*.pem
*.key

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/